For a better understanding of the present invention and in order to show how the same may carried into effect, reference will now be made, by way of example, to the accompanying drawings, in which:


FIG. 1 illustrates beam propagation along a slab-type lasing medium;


FIG. 2 shows a longitudinal cross-section through a solid state laser employing a slab-type lasing medium;


FIG. 3 shows a transverse cross-section through the solid state laser of FIG. 2; and


FIG. 4 shows a transverse cross-section through an alternative slab-type lasing medium suitable for use in the laser of FIGS. 2 and 3.
